snippet.title: The R.O.O.T.S Trailer
snippet.description:
The R.O.O.T.S is a real-time strategy game. 
Defeat enemy trees and war down all planets! 
It's a little similar to games like Galcon, Eufloria or Tentacle Wars. 
http://www.remaginarium.com/
